<h1 class="govuk-heading-l">UK Market Conformity Assessment Bodies</h1>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">

    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
        <p class="govuk-body">
            The UK Market Conformity Assessment Bodies (UKMCAB) database
            serves as the UK's database of Conformity Assessment Bodies (CABs).
            UKMCAB is part of the
            <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy">
                Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy
            </a>.
            It is the definitive source and a register of UK Government
            appointed CABs who can certify goods for both the GB and NI markets.
        </p>
        <p class="govuk-body">
            If there are any issues with the accuracy of the information in UKMCAB,
            please let us know at <a class="govuk-link" href="mailto:approvedbodies@beis.gov.uk">approvedbodies@beis.gov.uk</a>
        </p>

        <nav>
            <ul class="govuk-list">
                <li class="govuk-!-margin-top-9">
                    <a class="govuk-link govuk-!-font-weight-bold" href="@Url.RouteUrl(HomeController.Routes.Search)">Find a CAB</a>
                    <p class="govuk-!-margin-top-0">Find accredited Conformity Assessment Bodies (CABs) for your product.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="govuk-!-margin-top-9 govuk-!-margin-bottom-9">
                    <a class="govuk-link govuk-!-font-weight-bold" href="#!">Contact</a>
                    <p class="govuk-!-margin-top-0">Contact us to find out how we can help you.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>

        </nav>

    </div>

</div>


